				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Sky Shrine Cobalt Scar Key Quest<a name="24024"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 26 04 9:35 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Corgar:
<br />

<br />
Mukabre is right on to get to POM.  You arrive on a see-through platform, which is far enough from the mobs in the forest (yellow and red to me at 51) to reapply invis (I use the song of travel).
<br />

<br />
Then start clicking trees.  Once you see the message &quot;You are too far away to target this&quot; or something like that, you are in the right direction.  Use that to zero in on the right tree until you port to CS.
<br />

<br />
Once in CS, you will be underwater.  I turn EAST, swimming to the surface, and then reapply Song of Travel.  I run to the beach, turn around to make sure no shark or anything aggroed and followed me in, and then go about my business.
<br />

<br />
What a time saver.  Even with the SS/CS key I use this to get there.
<br />

<br />
Badji</span></td>
